title: For Sale/Trade:  Parts / Project set Westernfield 59a Springfield 87a Stevens 6a gill rifle
postcontent: Barreled receiver with trigger, magazine, and shell lifter for Westernfield 59a rifle. Equivalent to a Springfield/Stevens /Savage Model 87A, Ranger 101, Savage Model 6, and other models. Semi-automatic tube-fed .22LR. Vintage rifle with very interesting mechanism. Known as a "Gill Rifle" for the unique venting slots on the side. This is nearly a complete rifle and essentially just needs the stock and the inner magazine tube. There is an inner tube included that is slightly too long, it could be modified or you could find an original matching one. I was going to convert this to a bullpup but don't have time. It could also be fit into a modified airsoft shell, carve your own stock, or some other custom project. It appears to be fully functional, the bolt cocks and fires. I have not tested with live rounds but don't see any reason it would not work. The Bluing is faded with age but there is no major rust or pitting that I can see. Appears to be drilled and tapped for two-bolt side scope mount. I will sell for $100 or will consider trades for a .22 revolver or other guns. The parts alone are worth $125+ on ebay without the receiver.

title: For Sale:  Do You Know How To Handle A Home Invasion?
postcontent: Let’s face the cold hard facts – when seconds count, the Police Officer is only minutes away.You have heard this, but it’s very true, and most police officers will agree with this statement 100%. Do you know what to do to protect your family from a home invasion? What if that bad guy has a gun pointed at your wife or daughter’s head? What then?If you do what the movies and TV always show, you are pretty much guaranteeing that you will watch your wife die, probably after worse happens, and that will be your dying thought … that you SHOULD have done something – anything.Ready Defense Labs is the ONLY force on force, simulated event firearms training in Oklahoma that is focused on delivering long-term practical defensive firearm training, hands-on practice and force on force simulated events taken from news headlines and actual events. We recreate these events so our students can experience them first hand; learning skills and techniques they can immediately apply should they ever have to face a similar traumatic event in real life.This is NOT a CCW class or a legal course – these will be courses designed to teach fundamental defensive tactics to civilians in the same manner practiced by law enforcement, military and first responders.You can read books and watch movies or videos online, but NOTHING replaces the invaluable experience of hands on training, where you get to learn in real time, learn from other’s mistakes and practice in a controlled, live fire environment.If you are interested in learning how to protect yourself and loved ones and want to take your CCW to the next level without breaking the bank then follow this link to pre-register for Ready Defense Labs Grand Opening in Summer 2017.http://ReadyDefenseLabs.com

title: For Sale:  Rossi 62A slide action, take-down 22 rifle, Winchester 62 clone
postcontent:
Rossi 62A slide action, take-down 22 rifle, Winchester 62 clone.
Clone of the popular Winchester “Gallery Gun” originally made in the early 1900s. The Gallery Gun was the preferred rifle for use in shooting galleries, carnivals and fairs because it was rugged yet light weight, fun to shoot, and it has a one screw take down feature for ease in storing and transporting. 
Many of the original or “Slide action” as they were known back in the day, only fired 22 gallery loads and 22 shorts. Often, the modern day clones by Interarms, and the Rossi rifles that followed, are only chambered for Long Rifle.
This one is the improved version and it is labeled to shoot Shorts, Long and Long Rifle loads.
This particular rifle is un-modified, in great shape, has very nice wood and shows little wear. Since they haven’t made them in many years, you are very unlikely to see another one in this condition.
In addition to having the ability to shoot a wide variety of ammo, a 30 second takedown, slim profile and being very light weight, this model has the neat feature that allows you to hold down the trigger and fire the rifle as fast as you can slide the action.
This would be a great rifle for an experienced shooter looking for a reliable travel or survival rifle that is also fun to shoot. While the light weight, pump action with visible hammer also makes it a great beginner’s rifle.
The ability to shoot most 22 ammo, a reliable pump action, and the simple take down feature would also make it a great “Just-in-case” rifle to tuck away somewhere. Cypress area. For more questions:  REDACTED, voice or text.
